{"tid":1676953,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"法律界嘅朋友麻煩入嚟，呢條線要反攻","createTime":"2019-10-26T18:23:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T01:24:44.000Z","uid":34705,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"fae91633d310cd72e5d4a289afecf7d47e435863","tid":1676953,"uid":34705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T18:23:45.000Z","msg":"明白已經有唔少人幫緊被補義士處理法律程序，但係近期政府同 popo 都 keep 住出咗幾條反起底嘅禁制令，變相令班狗又多一堆武器搞我哋。老實啲講喺法律呢條線係輸到仆街...<br />\n<br />\n喺連練跑都要你申請不反對通知書嘅呢一刻，請用行動證明抗爭者唔係 condom，連最基本咁去 challenge 個禁制令都冇就真係講唔通，義士們拋個身出嚟撐，係時候靠法律界嘅你哋行多一步.<br />\n<br />\n就算係機會唔大甚至會輸，都可以轉化成不義政權操控嘅罪證！如果我哋之行動升級亦出師有名，甚至推上 Tweeter 拉埋班法官落水！<br />\n<br />\n麻煩晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7008b7c34a151630898a9a6dd6d9fb6711f240d","tid":1676953,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T18:24:05.000Z","msg":"可唔可以唔好剩係懲罰出名嘅黃店？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675556\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675556</a>"},{"pid":"0cb58b893185852a4ea454ee33a82e9dd9341a46","tid":1676953,"uid":34705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T18:25:22.000Z","msg":"如果各位覺得有道理嘅，請幫手一齊推，唔該！"},{"pid":"f82ee9f6af3c6151abe1c243af457391b2484c3a","tid":1676953,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T18:25:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>主線速遞</strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">星期日 10 &middot; 27 </span><br />\n追究警暴 守護民眾記者 守護穆斯林</strong></span><br />\n- 15:00 尖沙咀梳士巴利道公園<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">星期日 10 &middot; 27</span><br />\n自由之鶴追悼